Summary: Object appeared to be traveling NW in the sky along a straight path.
divs: sighting detailsi was on my back porch having coffee watching the birds fly around, when i noticed a one was not flapping it's wings. the birds landed but the object in sky did not. it was v-shaped, but slightly more rounded like a boomerang. the color was dark dull charcoal black\grey, not shinny at all, no lights,no sound of an engine, and no contrail. it was traveling north west, but it was very high in the sky, not at the height most airplanes fly in this area. this is not the flight pattern that i see other planes flying at either. the object seemed to be traveling along a straight line of flght. i watched it until it went out of my sight. this was on a very clear, sunny day, very few clouds in the sky. watched it for about 2 minutes.
